courses.title: HTML & CSS
courses.description: HTML is the foundation behind all web pages. It’s used to add structure and form to text, images, and more. CSS is the language used to style HTML content. In this first course, you’ll learn the fundamentals of both languages so that you can create visually appealing web pages.

courses.title: JavaScript
courses.description: JavaScript is among the most powerful and flexible programming languages of the web. It powers the dynamic behavior on most websites, including this one.
